title: Without Me
author: Halsey
lyrics:
[00:13.95] Found you when your heart was broke
[00:17.98] I filled your cup until it overflowed
[00:20.97] Took it so far to keep you close (keep you close)
[00:25.06] I was afraid to leave you on your own
[00:27.97] Said I'd catch you if you fall (fall)
[00:31.36] And if they laugh, then fuck 'em all (all)
[00:34.73] And then I got you off your knees
[00:36.81] Put you right back on your feet
[00:38.65] Just so you can take advantage of me
[00:41.84] Tell me, how's it feel sitting up there?
[00:45.08] Feeling so high but too far away to hold me
[00:48.75] You know I'm the one who put you up there
[00:52.19] Name in the sky, does it ever get lonely?
[00:55.82] Thinking you could live without me
